BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 703 Tm (- SPEC is a React/Vite furniture sourcing app built on Base44.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 692 Tm (- It combines manufacturer search, comparison, cart/order routing, and catalog workflows in one interface.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 675 Tm (Who It's For) Tj ET
