BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 649 Tm (- Repo evidence also includes admin, manufacturer, buyer/consumer roles.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 632 Tm (What It Does) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 617 Tm (- Natural-language AI search calls aiSearchProducts and returns ranked manufacturer results.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 606 Tm (- Dashboard highlights listing volume, styles, manufacturers, commissions, and lead times.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 595 Tm (- Compare up to 4 listings side by side across price, commission, lead time, material, and dimensions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 584 Tm (- Browse manufacturer profiles with active SKU counts, categories, and lead-time ranges.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 573 Tm (- View product detail with role-based pricing, specs, reviews, inventory, and add-to-cart.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 562 Tm (- Create cart orders; checkout writes Order records and clears CartItem records.) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 551 Tm (- Manufacturer/admin pages support catalog management, CSV import, and order visibility.) Tj ET
