BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 42 519 Tm (- Frontend: React 18 + Vite SPA with auto-registered routes from src/pages.config.js and shared layout/auth) Tj ET
BT /F1 9 Tf 1 0 0 1 52 508 Tm (wrappers.) Tj ET
